txt.en: Kill enemy guards on the Ornendil Bridge ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Shíktarb is at Shrak Mauruk.\n\nYou should listen to Shíktarb yell at you.
'Go to the Northern bridge, called the Ornendil and get rid of those pesky guards. Send those Men to their deaths. I want that bridge under Morgul control today!'
Listen to Shíktarb yell at you
Shíktarb commands you to kill enemy guards on the Ornendil Bridge for the glory of conquering their land.

'Well I'm impressed! You managed to kill all those guards?! Sounds like you caused some real damage!\n\n'Hope you didn't bring down the bridge! We'll need that bridge if we're to take and hold the Palace of Eldacar!'
Ornendil Bridge is located in Northern Osgiliath over the Anduin River.\n\nYou should kill enemy guards on the Ornendil Bridge.
